resources.string: An upcoming, feature-rich premium Android music player, currently in early development, built on the foundational design principles of Inure App Manager.

An elegant and beautiful premium Android app manager with both root and Shizuku support, a built-in terminal, analytics, VirusTotal support and an independent custom theme engine, developed with purely custom APIs created for this app.
An elegant and colorful location information app for Android with Compass, Clock, Level, Sun, Moon, Trail Marker and many other features.
